          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Barcelona</placeName>
                                        <date>Janry 18th/53</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Is Leeser Esqr.</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <placeName>Philadpa</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Revd. Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Your valued note of the <date>15<hi rend="sup"
                                                  >th</hi></date> ulto. was recd &amp; duly
                                        no<lb/>ticed together with the proof sheet, the size of
                                        which, is more porta<lb/>ble than those your last edition,
                                        excepting the quality of paper, which<lb/> I found to be a
                                        little inferior; my subscribers, thro' my organ,<lb/> begs
                                        to have equal quality as the set of Parasa &amp; Prayer<lb/>
                                        Books which I hold here of your first Edition, that is,
                                        “with<lb/> no additional cost.”</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I am truly sorry that I cannot prove of more<lb/>
                                        service to yr valued Periodical the Occident &amp; moreso to
                                        feel<lb/> the justice of your observation; for tho' few, we
                                        (they) feel very<lb/> little interest in the genl. cause of
                                        Judaism—As far<lb/> as concerns myself, I doubt not you will
                                        send or continue<lb/> sending the nos. &amp; inform me thro
                                        what channel you would<lb/> like them import to be remitted
                                        to you—<sic>wether</sic> Lag<add>?</add><lb/> or
                                                  <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>.<add>?</add>
                                        Revd. Sr. I remain</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">respectfully yours,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">
                                        <persName role="author">Saml Piza</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>P.S. Please stamp no name on the covers of the set orderd<lb/> for
                                                  <persName>A. H. Moro</persName>.</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>To the</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <addressee>Revd. Is. Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">
                                        <placeName>Philada.</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p>care of <persName>Messr A. M.</persName></p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <persName>Seixas &amp; Co.</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">via</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">
                                        <placeName>La Gu<add>?</add></placeName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
